@page sspatch sspatch

Modify a table/database/spreadsheet to integrate the changes described in a pre-computed difference.



\section sspatch_usage Usage
 \li sspatch [options] DATAFILE PATCHFILE
 \li sspatch [options] --cmd PATCHSTRING DATAFILE


